com.sri.ai.util.collect

Class PairOfElementsInListIterator<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sri.ai.util.collect.EZIterator<PairOf<E>>
      • com.sri.ai.util.collect.PairOfElementsInListIterator<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - the type of elements
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.Iterator<PairOf<E>>

    @Beta
public class PairOfElementsInListIterator<E>
extends EZIterator<PairOf<E>>
    An iterator over pairs of distinct elements in an List, such that each pair's first element occurs before the second in the list. It is highly advisable that the list be an ArrayList since the class heavily uses random access.

    braz
